    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Islamic legal scholars solicited by judges to weigh in on cases. Although non-binding, the muftis' reponse is considered authoritative and upheld in most instances.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
